<b>Sri Vidya Mandir Secondary School</b> was started on 07.06.1978. It is affiliated to the central board of secondary education, New Delhi. We prepare students for the All India Secondary School examination conducted by the Central board of secondary education.</br></br>The school is managed by a educational trust by name Sri Vidya Mandir Educational trust (Registered), with Sri .C. Mohanlal sowcar as its Founder chairman.The school offers sound education with emphasis on discipline, character building and leadership qualities. The school offers education through English medium.</br></br>Hindi and Tamil are the languages taught in our school.  The school when started had just four hundred students. Now our strength is four thousand three hundred. We have all infrastructural facilities for a thriving school.</br></br>